    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/ece2f2b10ef1b254369a1a4194f0c15c.avif?t=1758378495\" width=400 height=78 /></span><br>A merge puzzle game in which you combine round cats to make bigger round cats!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/e0c8b8782307f552077370b20e74d8d5.poster.avif?t=1758378495\" width=500 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/e0c8b8782307f552077370b20e74d8d5.webm?t=1758378495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/e0c8b8782307f552077370b20e74d8d5.mp4?t=1758378495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/52fa27fb61d6a80b33ef0fcb14f184f1.avif?t=1758378495\" width=400 height=78 /></span><br>In classic mode you can play the classic suika/watermelon experience. You drop a cat and, if the cat touches another cat of the same size, they will merge into a larger cat. Try to create the biggest cat possible but, if the cats reach the limit of the container, it will be game over.<br>This is similar to the original suika game, but with a few tweaks in the physics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/4036c721d5f8996cd4715b493bc5290a.avif?t=1758378495\" width=400 height=78 /></span><br>In daily variant you play with special rules. <br>Each day there can be up to three special rules such as<strong> low gravity, bouncy cats, time limits</strong>, and more.<br>Play every day to discover them all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/0e29d82eab5c2ab0645266e536eb3ba4.poster.avif?t=1758378495\" width=500 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/0e29d82eab5c2ab0645266e536eb3ba4.webm?t=1758378495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/0e29d82eab5c2ab0645266e536eb3ba4.mp4?t=1758378495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/15fb10462f1a0a42746394223c8f3248.avif?t=1758378495\" width=400 height=78 /></span><br>Climb the leaderboard in the classic mode or try to be the star of the day by competing in the daily variant, where a new leaderboard is created every day.",
